      "text": "たまにね、泣きたくなっちゃうんだ\n挫けたりはしないけど、悔しいじゃない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sometimes‚ I just feel like crying.\nI’m not giving up‚ but it still hurts‚ you know…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 209.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
