      "text": "私みたいな地味な子がアイドルなんて笑っちゃうよね\nでも、私……やっぱりアイドルになりたいの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "An ordinary girl like me wanting to be an idol—it’s laughable‚ right?\nBut still… I really want to be an idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 221.0666656494,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
