      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ、オーディションの練習付き合います\nだから……だから、一緒に頑張りましょう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s it! I’ll practice auditions with you.\nSo… so let’s do our best together!",
        "id": ""
